ave%20rigorous%20and%20fair%20recruitment%20processes%20that%20don't%20allow%20nepotism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20it's%20often%20hard%20to%20ensure%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-name-resume-hired-guilty-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpartial%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20always%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTools%20such%20as%20'blind%20CVs'%20%E2%80%94%20where%20an%20applicant's%20personal%20details%20are%20removed%20from%20their%20job%20application%20%E2%80%94%20exist%2C%20or%20a%20ban%20on%20hiring%20senior%20management's%20immediate%20family%20exists%20to%20try%20to%20reduce%20nepotism%2C%20particularly%20in%20certain%20industries%20that%20have%20historically%20been%20prone%20to%20it%2C%20such%20as%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Salton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20leveraging%20connections%20isn't%20all%20that%20different%20from%20relying%20on%20other%20talents%20or%20qualities%20that%20one%20has%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allisonching.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllison%20Ching%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20life%20and%20career%20coach%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20possess%20different%20types%20of%20arrows%20in%20our%20quiver%3A%20some%20of%20us%20are%20blessed%20with%20high%20IQ%2C%20some%20with%20specific%20talents%2C%20and%20some%20with%20rich%20and%20well-connected%20parents.%20It%20is%20acceptable%20to%20use%20what%20we%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Ching%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20parental%20connections%2C%20or%20any%20other%20arrows%20in%20our%20quiver%2C%20should%20be%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20at%20best%2C%20but%20never%20as%20a%20crutch%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229847c634-b8c2-4405-98e6-21277aea35ec%5C%22%3EPulling%20your%20weight%20at%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20people%20be%20open%20about%20their%20family%20connections%20at%20work%2C%20then%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E