%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raju%20also%20alleged%20he%20was%20subjected%20to%20%26quot%3Bcustodial%20torture%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20five%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20were%20charged%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20as%20the%20allegations%20pointed%20to%20a%20case%20that%20happened%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raju%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%202021%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20alleged%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20officials%20%26quot%3Bplotted%26quot%3B%20a%20criminal%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20false%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20me%20by%20the%20CB-CID%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government.%20On%20May%2014%2C%202021%2C%20I%20was%20arrested%20without%20due%20process%2C%20I%20was%20bullied%2C%20unlawfully%20physically%20pulled%20inside%20the%20police%20vehicle%2C%20and%20forcibly%20taken%20to%20Guntur%20the%20same%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raju%20alleged%20in%20the%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Raju%20was%20arrested%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20heading%20the%20CID%2C%20Mr%20Sitaramanjaneyulu%20the%20intelligence%20wing%2C%20Mr%20Paul%20was%20assistant%20superintendent%20of%20police%20CID%20and%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20said%20though%20he%20had%20undergone%20an%20open%20heart%20surgery%20%26quot%3Bsome%20weeks%26quot%3B%20before%20his%20arrest%2C%20Mr%20Raju%20claimed%20he%20was%20abused.%20Also%2C%20he%20alleged%20there%20were%20threats%20to%20kill%20him%20for%20%26quot%3Bcriticising%20the%20chief%20minister%20(Jagan).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20arrested%20without%20due%20process%2C%20including%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20medical%20examination%20or%20adherence%20to%20proper%20legal%20procedures...%20I%20was%20kept%20in%20the%20CB-CID%20office%2C%20Guntur%20from%209%3A30%20pm%20onwards%20(May%2014%2C%202021).%20I%20was%20not%20given%20my%20medicine%20despite%20having%20had%20an%20open%20heart%20bypass%20surgery%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raju%20alleged%20when%20the%20magistrate%20sent%20him%20to%20Guntur%20Government%20General%20Hospital%2C%20the%20then%20superintendent%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20Prabhavathi%2C%20colluded%20with%20Sunil%20Kumar%20to%20create%20false%20medical%20reports%20that%20no%20injuries%20were%20inflicted%20on%20his%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20police%20brutality%2C%20I%20was%20shifted%20from%20Guntur%20to%20Secunderabad%20Army%20Hospital%20by%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20thereafter%20I%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720778940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7mhanj8k_jagan-reddy-650_625x300_31_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempt-to-murder-case-against-former-andhra-chief-minister-jagan-reddy-6090030%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20attempt%20to%20murder%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20and%20two%20India%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempt-to-murder-case-against-former-andhra-chief-minister-jagan-reddy-6090030%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempt-to-murder-case-against-former-andhra-chief-minister-jagan-reddy-6090030%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempt-to-murder-case-against-former-andhra-chief-minister-jaga