untries%20due%20to%20its%20year-round%20mild%20weather.%20She%20said%20it's%20also%20an%20hour's%20drive%20to%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20and%20three%20hours%20to%20the%20Caribbean%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20lived%20on%20the%20farm%20with%20her%20husband%20for%2012%20years%2C%20building%20a%20greenhouse%20where%20she%20grew%20organic%20food.%20When%20her%20husband%20died%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20a%20nearby%20home%20that%20required%20less%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20temperature%20stays%20around%2075%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20daily%2C%20though%20it%20feels%20cooler%20during%20the%20summer%20rainy%20season%20%E2%80%94%20she%20estimates%20her%20area%20gets%20almost%20200%20inches%20of%20rain%20a%20year.%20She's%20adjusted%20her%20schedule%20to%20get%20her%20errands%20done%20in%20the%20morning%20so%20she's%20inside%20when%20the%20rain%20starts%20in%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22181204d9-e41b-467e-b073-443b88ae6267%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Accidentally'%20starting%20a%20tour%20company%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELange%20had%20the%20budget%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-xers-financial-independence-retire-early-fire-started-saving-late-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretire%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Panama%2C%20but%20after%20giving%20her%20first%20tour%20to%20eight%20of%20her%20real%20estate%20investor%20friends%20similar%20to%20her%20solo%20tour%2C%20some%20of%20their%20friends%20began%20calling%20her%20about%20getting%20on%20her%20tours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20plan%20to%20start%20the%20business%20at%20all%2C%20so%20every%20time%20I%20did%20a%20tour%2C%20I%20learned%20something%20new%20that%20I%20wish%20I%20would%20have%20included%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Lange%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20it%20happened%20exactly%2C%20but%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20looking%20to%20move%20someplace%20else%2C%20because%20of%20the%20videos%20I%20had%20and%20the%20articles%20I%20wrote%2C%20would%20call%20me%20and%20ask%20me%20questions.%20The%20business%20just%20grew%20pretty%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20crafted%20a%20website%20herself%20and%20started%20advertising%20on%20expat%20groups.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20organized%20the%20tours%20based%20on%20her%20itinerary%20when%20she%20first%20came%20to%20Panama%2C%20including%20the%20beach%20communities%2C%20urban%20centers%2C%20and%20mountain%20towns.%20Her%20tours%20included%20meetings%20with%20immigration%20attorneys%20and%20tourism%20leaders%20who%20could%20share%20information%20about%20getting%20a%20residency%20visa%2C%20as%20well%20as%20meetups%20with%20other%20expats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20she%20researched%20more%20ways%20to%20avoid%20costly%20mistakes%2C%20from%20how%20to%20buy%20a%20car%20to%20taking%20care%20of%20pets.%20She%20added%20more%20information%20about%20rentals%2C%20as%20she%20said%20sometimes%20homes%20under%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20may%20lack%20amenities%20like%20hot%20water.%20She%20gives%20participants%20a%20list%20of%2017%20questions%20to%20ask%20before%20renting%20a%20house%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20it%20has%20a%20reserve%20water%20tank%20in%20case%20of%20a%20drought.%20Lange%20advises%20expats%20not%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20until%20they've%20rented%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20kids%20joined%20the%20business%20and%20now%20handle%20the%20logistics%20and%20marketing.%20After%2010%20years%20of%20leading%20the%20tours%20herself%2C%20she%20recruited%20expat%20tour%20guides%20and%20Panamanian%20bus%20drivers%20to%20help%20run%20group%20and%20private%20tours.%20She%20also%20crafted%20an%20online%20relocation%20guide%20with%20information%20on%20health%20insurance%20companies%2C%20private%20hospitals%2C%20CPAs%2C%20shipping%20and%20moving%20companies%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she's%20increasingly%20received%20emails%20from%20people%20saying%20they're%20supposed%20to%20retire%20in%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%20US%20but%20can't%20afford%20it%20and%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20She's%20guided%20people%20nervous%20about%20finances%20to%20move%20to%20Panama%2C%20and%20many%20of%20her%20clients%20told%20her%20they're%20less%20stressed%20about%20making%20ends%20meet.%20She%20also%20said%20she's%20noticed%20people's%20health%20improve%20after%20moving%20to%20Panama%2C%20as%20they're%20often%20less%20stressed%20and%20eat%20healthier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20retire%20tomorrow%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%2C%20and%20we%20wouldn't%20skip%20a%20beat%2C%26quot%3B%20Lange%20said%2C%20noting%20she%20intends%20to%20keep%20the%20business%20running%20since%20most%20days%20don't%20feel%20like%20work.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20helping%20people%20who%20are%20feeling%20like%20it's%20a%20hopeless%2C%20helpless%20situation%20and%20showing%20them%20there%20is%20a%20solution%2C%20there%20is%20a%20way%20to%20take%20all%20that%20stress%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203cec1be-6ac5-411d-a23d-58c73dd5a066%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheaper%20living%20in%20Panama%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20sold%20her%20farmhouse%2C%20she%20moved%20into%20a%20three-bedroom%2C%20two-bath%20rental%20property%20for%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%20The%20home%20is%20fully%20furnished%20with%20all%20utilities%20included%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20gardener%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20has%20modern%20appliances%20with%20high-speed%20internet.%20She%20said%20she's%20seen%20towns%20nearby%20with%20furnished%20one-bedroom%20rentals%20for%20%24250%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20spends%20about%20%2480%20a%20week%20on%20groceries%20and%20cat%20food%20and%20mostly%20shops%20at%20local%20farmer's%20markets.%20She%20paid%20%2420%2C000%20for%20her%202020%20Hyundai%20Santa%20Fe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20pays%20%242%2C788%20a%20year%20for%20health%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.internationalinsurance.com%2Fhealth%2Fnorth-america%2Fpanama%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20covers%20100%25%20of%20hospital%20and%20emergency%20room%20visits%20worldwide.%20Without%20insurance%2C%20many%20routine%20doctor%20visits%20are%20%2415.%20A%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20she%20got%20her%20teeth%20cleaned%20and%20received%20X-rays%20for%20%2442.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20prices%20vary%20significantly%20across%20the%20country.%20Homes%20in%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Coronado%2C%20which%20has%20many%20expats%2C%20can%20sell%20for%20three%20times%20the%20price%20of%20similar%20homes%20in%20beachfront%20communities%20with%20fewer%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20choices%20to%20live%20by%20the%20expat%20community%2C%20where%20it%20might%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20on%20a%20tight%20budget%2C%20you%20can%20move%20to%20a%20town%20an%20hour%20away%2C%2030%20minutes%20away%2C%20where%20the%20prices%20could%20be%2050%25%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Lange%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20left%20the%20United%20States%20for%20a%20new%20country%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-moving-texas-panama-retirement-cheaper-tourism-weather-social-security-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720778282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d5eb71aace5b3ada56328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-moving-texas-panama-retirement-cheaper-tourism-weather-social-security-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20moving%20from%20Texas%20to%20Panama%20for%20her%20retirement%2C%20Jackie%20Lange%20started%20Panama%20Reloca