%3E%3Cp%3EI%20inadvertently%20learned%20I%20was%20diabetic%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%20during%20a%20routine%20physical%20appointment%20in%20my%20early%2020s%20when%20my%20triglycerides%20had%20suddenly%20skyrocketed%20to%20dangerous%20levels.%20My%20primary%20care%20physician%20did%20more%20blood%20work%2C%20diagnosed%20me%20with%20insulin%20resistance%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fwhat-causes-type-2-diabetes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etype%202%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20swiftly%20sent%20me%20to%20a%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac887612-573f-4180-ba54-da08a5b73d76%5C%22%3EA%20specialist%20diagnosed%20me%20with%20type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20over%20nine%20months%20of%20working%20with%20a%20specialist%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-went-to-5-doctors-before-i-was-diagnosed-with-type-1-diabetes-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediagnosed%20with%20type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20type%202.%20The%20primary%20difference%20is%20that%20the%20bodies%20of%20people%20with%20type%202%20diabetes%20produce%20insulin%20and%20can't%20effectively%20process%20it.%20In%20contrast%2C%20people%20with%20type%201%20don't%20produce%20insulin%2C%20so%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20injected%20subcutaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20was%20first%20diagnosed%2C%20my%20entire%20life%20changed.%20I%20was%20markedly%20ashamed%20of%20the%20disease.%20I%20saw%20the%20way%20diabetes%20was%20described%20in%20mainstream%20media%20as%20something%20that%20primarily%20affected%20people%20who%20were%20overweight.%20And%20I've%20always%20been%20overweight.%20Though%20it's%20type%202%20diabetes%20that%20was%20medically%20linked%20with%20obesity%2C%20I%20still%20worried%20most%20people%20didn't%20know%20the%20nuance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiet-and-exercise-strategies-for-lower-blood-sugar-reverse-type-2-diabetes-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediabetic%20diagnoses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20would%20make%20assumptions%20about%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fda0064-4a83-4066-b908-350bada1c2ee%5C%22%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20I%20felt%20shame%20about%20my%20diagnosis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20first%20years%20of%20my%20diagnosis%20isolated%20in%20shame.%20I%20wore%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsulin-price-cap-costs-diabetes-supplies-pump-monitor-tiktok-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsulin%20pump%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20my%20clothing.%20The%20bulky%20device%20clipped%20into%20my%20bra%20and%20was%20tethered%20to%20the%20injection%20site%20by%20a%20long%2C%20clear%20tube%20that%20got%20caught%20on%20everything.%20I%20started%20hugging%20people%20at%20a%20distance%2C%20worried%20they'd%20feel%20it%20pressing%20on%20them.%20I%20went%20to%20education%20classes%20on%20medical%20equipment%20required%20by%20my%20insurance%20carrier.%20But%20I%20didn't%20identify%20as%20a%20diabetic%20internally%20to%20myself%2C%20or%20to%20others.%20I%20wanted%20to%20keep%20my%20condition%20at%20an%20emotional%20distance%2C%20even%20from%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20got%20a%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%2C%20but%20it%20was%20conspicuous%2C%20either%20on%20the%20back%20of%20my%20arm%20or%20presenting%20as%20a%20visible%20lump%20under%20my%20waistline.%20I%20hated%20getting%20questions%20at%20the%20gym%20when%20I%20wore%20a%20tank%20top%3A%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20what's%20that%20for%3F%26quot%3B%20Or%20from%20the%20woman%20fitting%20my%20wedding%20dress%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20want%20to%20pick%20a%20different%20style%20if%20you%20wear%20%3Cem%3Ethis%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20big%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261cc01b1-3346-476c-8846-13fd9f077746%5C%22%3EEventually%2C%20my%20perspective%20changed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20another%20decade%20to%20slowly%20let%20people%20in%20on%20my%20diabetic%20secret.%20I%20realized%20that%20for%20every%20prying%20question%2C%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20that%20for%20allergies%3F%26quot%3B%20followed%20by%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20you%20were%20DI-A-BE-TIC!%20(gasp)%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20I'd%20give%20the%20answer%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethere%20was%20rarely%20a%20follow-up.%20People%20were%20curious%20about%20the%20medical%20equipment%2C%20but%20the%20deriding%20comments%20I%20was%20afraid%20of%20often%20didn't%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it%20was%20wisdom%20that%20came%20with%20age%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20I%20simply%20stopped%20caring%20what%20other%20people%20thought%20about%20my%20condition%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcosts-to-manage-type-1-diabetes-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20I%20was%20managing%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20doing%20great%2C%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20A1C%20%E2%80%94%20which%20measures%20average%20blood%20glucose%20levels%20over%20three%20months%20%E2%80%94%20under%206.1%25.%20This%20was%20down%20from%209.1%25%20when%20I%20was%20first%20diagnosed%3B%20for%20context%2C%20a%20non-diabetic%20A1C%20is%20around%205.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOwning%20the%20emotional%20reality%20of%20my%20condition%20also%20helped%20me%20make%20better%20choices%20for%20my%20care.%20I%20switched%20from%20an%20insulin%20pump%20to%20shots%2C%20which%20makes%20me%20feel%20more%20in%20control%20of%20my%20dosing.%20I%20have%20authentic%20conversations%20when%20people%20ask%20me%20how%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhave-insulin-allergy-with-type-one-diabetes-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20my%20blood%20sugar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20the%20shame%20that%20kept%20me%20from%20hugging%20people%20years%20ago%2C%20scared%20they'd%20feel%20my%20insulin%20pump%2C%20had%20evaporated.%20Now%2C%20not%20only%20do%20I%20not%20care%20if%20people%20know%20I%20have%20diabetes%2C%20but%20sometimes%2C%20at%20business%20dinners%2C%20I%20pull%20out%20my%20insulin%20pens%2C%20screw%20in%20the%20needle%2C%20and%20push%20the%20required%20units%20into%20my%20belly%20right%20through%20my%20blouse%20at%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ward%20off%20prying%20questions%20with%20a%20confident%20smile%20and%20a%20remark%20that%20sends%20us%20back%20to%20the%20conversation%20at%20hand.%20I'm%20not%20as%20annoyed%20by%20inquiries%20as%20I%20once%20was%2C%20but%20I%20rarely%20speak%20at%20length%20with%20acquaintances%20or%20strangers.%20I%20reserve%20in-depth%20conversations%20for%20my%20partner%2C%20close%20friends%2C%20and%20endocrinology%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2020%20years%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20owning%20my%20condition%20means%20leaning%20into%20pragmatism%20rather%20than%20emotion.%20After%20all%2C%20I'm%20the%20one%20living%20with%20diabetes%2C%20not%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccepting-type-1-diabetes-insulin-shots-dinner-table-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720776123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668ff997b2528216eeb55b96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccepting-type-1-diabetes-insulin-shots-dinner-table-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20felt%20ashamed%20when%20I%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20type%201%20diabetes.%20Doing%20insulin%20shots%20in%20public%20helped%20me%20accept%20my%20diagnosis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Andrea%20Javor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccepting-type-1-diabetes-insulin-shots-dinner-table-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Latest%20Flash