E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F07%2F11%2Fus-news%2Fnursing-student-lauren-johansen-found-beaten-to-death-after-dads-chilling-warning-to-judge%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Johansen's%20former%20partner%2C%2023-year-old%20Bricen%20Rivers%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20her%20murder.%20He%20had%20been%20released%20on%20a%20bond%20just%20five%20days%20before%20the%2022-year-old's%20death.%20He%20was%20previously%20held%20for%20aggravated%20kidnapping%20for%20brutally%20beating%20Ms%20Johansen%20and%20holding%20her%20hostage%20during%20a%20December%20trip%20to%20Nashville.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Johansen%20was%20on%20track%20to%20get%20her%20nursing%20degree.%20She%20was%20first%20reported%20missing%20on%20July%202%20when%20her%20sister%20woke%20up%20alone%20in%20their%20shared%20apartment%20with%20the%20front%20door%20wide%20open%20and%20their%20security%20camera%20smashed.%20The%20same%20morning%2C%20her%20father%20said%20he%20woke%20up%20to%20a%20notification%20that%20her%20location-tracking%20app%20had%20been%20turned%20off.%20He%20then%20reported%20her%20missing%2C%20and%20the%20next%20day%2C%20officers%20informed%20him%20that%20they%20had%20located%20her%20car%20in%20a%20nearby%20cemetery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Johansen%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20her%20car%20which%20was%20parked%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20cemetery%20in%20Harrison%20County%2C%20Mississippi.%20Her%20mutilated%20body%20was%20wrapped%20up%20in%20trash%20bags%20over%20the%20back%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20basically%20beaten%20to%20death.%20Her%20face%20was%20smashed%20in%2C%20her%20head%20was%20smashed%20in%2C%20she%20was%20brutally%20beaten%20to%20the%20point%20she%20couldn't%20see%20out%20of%20either%20eye%20when%20she%20finally%20died%20and%20there%20was%20multiple%20holes%20in%20her%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Johansen's%20father%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20helped%20the%20coroner%20lift%20her%20body%20out%20of%20the%20car.%20It%20was%20just%20mutilated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchina-company-confines-employee-to-small-dark-room-for-4-days-heres-why-6089196%5C%22%3EChina%20Company%20Confines%20Employee%20To%20%26quot%3BSmall%20Dark%20Room%26quot%3B%20For%204%20Days.%20Here's%20Why%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20warned%20the%20judge%20that%20if%20her%20boyfriend%20was%20let%20out%20of%20jail%2C%20he%20would%20kill%20her.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Rivers%20had%20held%20his%20daughter%20hostage%20in%20December%20and%20beat%20her%20while%20the%20couple%20were%20on%20vacation%20in%20Nashville.%20He%20also%20added%20that%20in%20the%20moments%20leading%20to%20Rivers'%20December%20arrest%2C%20police%20officers%20found%20Lauren%20Johansen%20badly%20beaten%20and%20trying%20to%20escape%20a%20rental%20vehicle%20as%20Rivers%20reached%20for%20a%20firearm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heartbroken%20father%20slammed%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20in%20Tennessee%20for%20failing%20his%20family.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20in%20Nashville%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20failed%20my%20daughter%20and%20our%20family.%20The%20world%20shouldn't%20work%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20really%20beautiful%2C%20super%2C%20super%20smart.%20She%20had%20dreams%20and%20hopes%20that%20were%20larger%20than%20life.%20Everything%20she%20did%2C%20everything%20she%20touched%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Rivers%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20following%20a%20six-hour%20manhunt%2C%20faces%20a%20murder%20charge%20and%20is%20being%20held%20on%20a%20%241%20million%20bond.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720774080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim