d%20protests%20alleging%20that%20Gandhi's%20statue%20was%20removed%20to%20build%20a%20clock%20tower.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20met%20the%20municipal%20board%20and%20the%20town%20committee%2C%20they%20told%20us%20they%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20build%20clock%20tower%20but%20our%20question%20is%20why%20the%20civil%20society%20here%20was%20not%20taken%20into%20confidence%20before%20taking%20the%20decision%20to%20uproot%20the%20Gandhi%20statue%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Pritam%20Neog%2C%20an%20AASU%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Tushar%20Gandhi%2C%20great-grandson%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20had%20attacked%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Assam%20over%20the%20statue's%20removal.%20%26quot%3BNot%20surprising%20that%20the%20BJP%20Government%20in%20Assam%20decided%20to%20replace%20Bapu's%20statue%20with%20a%20clock%20tower%20in%20Dibrugarh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20oppose%20any%20city%20beautification%20project%20but%20it%20cannot%20be%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Gandhi's%20statue.%20We%20won't%20allow%20it.%20They%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20statue%20and%20build%20a%20clock%20tower%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20MLA%20Durga%20Bhumij%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20concerns%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Doomdooma%20Rupesh%20Gowala%20said%20that%20a%20new%20statue%20was%20being%20created%20and%20would%20be%20placed%20at%20the%20original%20site%20within%20six%20months.%20The%20new%20state%20would%20be%20a%20foot%20taller%20and%20would%20be%20placed%20next%20to%20a%20clock%20tower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20good%20for%20Doomdooma%20town%20to%20have%20a%20old%20broken%20statue%20of%20Gandhi%20ji%3F%20We%20removed%20it%20to%20replace%20with%20a%20taller%20and%20better%20statue%20and%20also%20to%20beautify%20the%20area%20around%20it%20but%20some%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20controversy%20and%20do%20politics%20over%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3