20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fbr-ambedkar-ap_650x403_41460966361.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election%20appear%20to%20mark%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20Dalit%20politics.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20sweeping%20departure%20from%20the%20traditional%20focus%20of%20Dalit%20politics%20on%20challenging%20India's%20entrenched%20caste-based%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20various%20Dalit%20political%20parties%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20in%20the%20north%2C%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(RPI)%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20others%20like%20the%20Viduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%20(VCK)%2C%20the%20All%20Manipur%20Dalit%20Development%20Association%2C%20the%20Puthiya%20Tamilagam%20(PT)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20the%20Praja%20Rajyam%20Party%20(PRP)%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20neighbouring%20states%2C%20have%20shaped%20Dalit%20political%20discourse%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20these%20parties%20have%20weakened%20over%20time%2C%20reflected%20in%20their%20diminished%20political%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20Wants%20The%20Dalit%20Vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20whether%20independent%20Dalit%20politics%20has%20a%20future%20in%20India%20is%20frequently%20debated.%20As%20India's%20democracy%20evolves%2C%20Dalits%20may%20increasingly%20assert%20themselves%20within%20the%20mainstream%20political%20landscape.%20Dalits%20constitute%2016.6%25%20of%20India's%20population%2C%20making%20their%20vote%20pivotal%20in%20shaping%20electoral%20outcomes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20are%20being%20aggressively%20courted%20by%20national%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20which%20is%20a%20crucial%20state%20in%20determining%20the%20national%20election%20results%20due%20to%20its%20significant%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20Dalits%20account%20for%2021.1%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20and%20thus%20their%20voting%20patterns%20are%20a%20critical%20area%20of%20study.%20In%20the%20recent%20elections%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20witnessed%20a%20departure%20from%20long-standing%20trends.%20Jatavs%2C%20a%20traditionally%20loyal%20group%20within%20the%20Dalit%20community%20known%20for%20their%20support%20for%20Mayawati's%20BSP%2C%20showed%20signs%20of%20shifting%20allegiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20segment%20of%20the%20BJP's%20core%20supporters%20and%20youth%2C%20who%20had%20remained%20faithful%20since%202014%2C%20switched%20their%20support%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)-Congress%20alliance%2C%20citing%20local%20issues%2C%20anti-incumbency%20sentiments%2C%20unemployment%20concerns%2C%20and%20apprehensions%20about%20constitutional%20amendments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20SP-Congress%20Alliance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20strategy%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20the%20Congress%20alliance%20in%20weaning%20Dalit%20votes%20away%20from%20the%20BSP%20in%20the%20recent%20elections%20exemplifies%20this%20shift.%20The%20alliance%20strategically%20fielded%20local%20candidates%2C%20further%20fragmenting%20the%20BSP's%20vote%20base.%20The%20SP's%20vote%20share%20rose%20from%2017.96%25%20in%202019%20to%2034%25%20in%202024%2C%20directly%20correlating%20with%20the%20BSP's%20decline%20from%2019%25%20to%209%25%20during%20the%20same%20period%2C%20leading%20to%20existential%20challenges%20for%20Mayawati's%20party.%20The%20entry%20of%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20into%20politics%20further%20fractures%20the%20Dalit%20movement%2C%20widening%20existing%20divides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20commanding%20victory%20in%20a%20four-way%20race%20involving%20his%20party%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20BSP%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%20further%20solidified%20his%20status%20as%20a%20rising%20Jatav%20youth%20icon.%20Similar%20Dalit%20voting%20trends%20can%20be%20observed%20across%20several%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20of%20the%202024%20election%20surprised%20many.%20However%2C%20a%20closer%20examination%20reveals%20that%20this%20stemmed%20from%20swing%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20became%20more%20local%20than%20national%2C%20affecting%20the%20BJP%20in%20around%2070%20seats.%20The%20Dalit%20vote%20also%20demonstrated%20a%20local%20focus%20in%20what%20was%20a%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Recalibrating%20Its%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20Dalit%20politics%20at%20an%20inflexion%20point%3F%20In%202024%2C%20Dalit%20votes%20were%20impacted%20by%20a%20number%20of%20factors.%20Political%20parties%20are%20swiftly%20moving%20to%20integrate%20Dalit%20politics%20into%20their%20platforms%2C%20recognising%20the%20emerging%20trend.%20They%20anticipate%20that%20Dalit%20votes%20will%20wield%20significant%20influence%20in%20the%202029%20elections%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20prompting%20a%20race%20among%20parties%20to%20establish%20early%20footholds.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20unit%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20Dalit%20%3Cem%3Echaupals%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Esammelans%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20engage%20community%20members%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20and%20consolidate%20its%20electoral%20gains%2C%20with%20a%20major%20outreach%20campaign%20slated%20for%20the%202027%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20actively%20recalibrating%20its%20strategy.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20elections%20and%20the%20period%20leading%20up%20to%202029%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20party%20to%20regain%20the%20complete%20confidence%20of%20Dalit%20voters.%20The%20direction%20forward%20hinges%20on%20the%20type%20of%20politics%20embraced%20-%20whether%20it%20is%20focused%20on%20empowerment%20or%20entitlement.%20Under%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20emphasised%20empowerment%20through%20initiatives%20like%20Nal%20se%20Jal%20and%20providing%20LPG%20connections%20and%20stoves%20to%20elevate%20living%20standards.%20Conversely%2C%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20placed%20emphasis%20on%20entitlement%20through%20direct%20cash%20transfers%20to%20individual%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20trajectory%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20the%20BJP%20refines%20or%20expands%20its%20welfare%20policies%2C%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20who%20emerges%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Dalits.%20Historically%2C%20Dalit%20women%20have%20been%20pivotal.%20But%20signs%20suggest%20that%20youth%20will%20increasingly%20shape%20the%20narrative%20leading%20up%20to%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20broadcast%20journalist%20and%20psephologist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720768620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fbr-ambedkar-ap_650x403_41460966361.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-dalit-politics-at-an-inflexion-point-6088987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20future%20trajectory%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20the%20BJP%20refines%20or%20expands%20its%20welfare%20policies%2C%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20who%20emerges%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Dalits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-dalit-politics-at-an-inflexion-point-6088987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww