67%5C%22%3ESan%20Fernando%3C%2Fa%3E'%2C%20a%20vessel%20from%20Maersk%2C%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20shipping%20company.%20The%20official%20inauguration%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Friday%2C%20and%20the%20port%20is%20expected%20to%20become%20fully%20operational%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%2010%20facts%20about%20Vizhinjam%20Port%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Vizhinjam%20has%20been%20an%20important%20port%20since%20ancient%20times%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20key%20maritime%20trade%20centre%20for%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Travancore.%20It%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20spice%20trade%2C%20connecting%20Kerala%20to%20global%20trade%20routes.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20The%20location%20of%20the%20port%20facilitated%20cultural%20and%20economic%20exchanges%20between%20Kerala%20and%20various%20civilizations%2C%20including%20the%20Greeks%2C%20Romans%2C%20Arabs%20and%20Chinese%2C%20which%20influenced%20the%20region's%20culture%2C%20cuisine%20and%20architecture.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20During%20the%20colonial%20period%2C%20Vizhinjam%20continued%20to%20be%20a%20critical%20port%20for%20European%20traders%2C%20including%20the%20Portuguese%2C%20Dutch%20and%20British%2C%20who%20competed%20for%20control%20over%20the%20spice%20trade%20in%20Kerala.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20In%20modern%20times%2C%20Vizhinjam's%20location%20near%20international%20shipping%20routes%20makes%20it%20a%20strategic%20point%20for%20maritime%20trade%2C%20reducing%20transit%20times%20for%20vessels.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20few%20natural%20deep-water%20ports%20in%20India%2C%20Vizhinjam%20can%20accommodate%20large%20cargo%20ships%20and%20container%20vessels%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20able%20to%20handle%20large-scale%20maritime%20trade%20efficiently.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn6.%20The%20development%20of%20the%20Vizhinjam%20International%20Seaport%20is%20expected%20to%20boost%20Kerala's%20economic%20growth%20by%20creating%20job%20opportunities%2C%20enhancing%20trade%20and%20attracting%20investments%20in%20the%20region.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn7.%20Ongoing%20infrastructure%20projects%20aim%20to%20equip%20Vizhinjam%20with%20state-of-the-art%20facilities%2C%20including%20modern%20container%20terminals%2C%20warehouses%20and%20logistics%20parks.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn8.%20The%20port%20is%20set%20to%20become%20a%20key%20player%20in%20regional%20trade%2C%20potentially%20serving%20as%20a%20gateway%20for%20trade%20between%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn9.%20Besides%20its%20commercial%20significance%2C%20Vizhinjam%20is%20known%20for%20its%20scenic%20beauty%20and%20potential%20for%20tourism%2C%20with%20the%20nearby%20Kovalam%20beach%20being%20a%20famous%20tourist%20destination.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn10.%20With%20its%20strategic%20location%20and%20modern%20infrastructure%2C%20Vizhinjam%20Port%20is%20expected%20to%20handle%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20trade%20volume%2C%20contributing%20to%20India's%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720764240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F87b06j78_vizhinjam-international-seaport-vessel_625x300_11_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvizhinjam-port-all-you-need-to-know-6088497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Vizhinjam%20Port%2C%20owned%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20is%20a%20strategic%20maritime%20project%20near%20Thiruvananthapuram%20in%20Kerala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvizhinjam-port-all-you-need-to-know-6088497%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Find