9t%20clear%20the%20Mains.%20This%20pattern%20continued%20in%20his%20successive%20attempts%20in%202015%20and%202016.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20clear%20the%20Mains%20but%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%20after%20the%20interview%20round.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unemployed%2C%20and%20I%20was%20not%20getting%20success%20in%20my%20attempts.%20I%20was%20disheartened%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20felt%20it%20was%20high%20time%20to%20work%20on%20his%20Plan%20B%20%E2%80%94%20securing%20a%20government%20position%20in%20the%20Punjab%20State%20Civil%20Services.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202017%2C%20I%20took%20up%20a%20job%20as%20an%20Inspector%20of%20Cooperative%20Society.%20This%20role%20allowed%20me%20to%20observe%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Government%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20It%20was%20an%20eye-opener%20for%20me.%20I%20realised%20that%20while%20civil%20services%20are%20often%20glamourised%2C%20the%20work%20of%20government%20officers%20is%20similar%20to%20any%20other%20job%2C%20with%20targets%20and%20goals%20to%20meet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsimran%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20UPSC-IFS.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A