th%20it%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20to%20make%20things%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cool%20thought%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20a%20Class%2011%20student%20at%20Navrachana%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Vadodara%20has%20innovated%3B%20albeit%20his%20creation%20is%20a%20miniaturised%2C%20robotic%20version%20of%20the%20said%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Meditel%E2%80%99%2C%20as%2015-year-old%20Nikhil%20Lemos%20has%20christened%20his%20brainchild%2C%20was%20born%20out%20of%20an%20innocent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330982%2Faditya-chaudhury-builds-neurosight-vaccivan-and-kalam-startup-to-help-student-innovators-with-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidea%20to%20help%20his%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20how%20they%20would%20sometimes%20forget%20to%20take%20their%20pills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20ideate%2C%20a%20young%20Nikhil%20put%20pen%20to%20paper%20and%20sketched%20what%20he%20assumed%20would%20be%20a%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20an%20alarm%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20was%20it%3B%20a%20doodle%20on%20the%20last%20page%20of%20a%20notebook.%20But%20a%20science%20fair%20at%20the%20end%20of%20term%20had%20him%20revisit%20this%20doodle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20innovative%20and%20I%20thought%20of%20going%20back%20to%20this%20idea.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20Meditel%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20innovation%20has%20grown%20with%20Nikhil%3B%20the%20two%20have%20shared%20a%20parallel%20journey%2C%20as%20the%20idea%20transcended%20from%20being%20a%20PowerPoint%20presentation%20to%20a%20paper%20model%20to%20a%20basic%20prototype.%20From%20there%20it%20transformed%20into%20a%20full-blown%20electrical%20model%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20nuances%20Nikhil%20found%20himself%20explaining%20to%20none%20other%20than%20football%20legend%20David%20Beckham%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20has%20been%20dream-like.%20And%20in%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Nikhil%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356097%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nikhil%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20just%20wanted%20to%20help%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20skipping%20one%E2%80%99s%20medicine%20dosage%20is%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20good%20health.%20But%20as%20Nikhil%20soon%20deduced%2C%20medication%20non-adherence%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20one-pronged%20problem.%20It%20had%20many%20facets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20an%20alarm%20system%20that%20would%20alert%20people%20when%20they%20needed%20to%20take%20their%20pills.%20But%2C%20eventually%2C%20as%20I%20observed%20my%20grandmother%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20even%20when%20she%20did%20remember%2C%20but%20did%20not%20have%20water%20handy%2C%20she%20would%20put%20it%20off%20for%20later.%E2%80%9D%20This%20led%20to%20Nikhil%20integrating%20a%20reusable%20water%20bottle%20into%20the%20device%2C%20attached%20by%20velcro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20component%20was%20the%20pill%20organiser%2C%20born%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20people%20who%20were%20prescribed%20multiple%20doses%20specific%20to%20their%20meal%20times.%20%E2%80%9CMeditel%20allows%20users%20to%20set%20up%20to%20six%20daily%20alarms%2C%20accommodating%20various%20medication%20schedules%20like%20pre%2Fpost%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20explains.%20Sourcing%20the%20parts%20and%20putting%20the%20device%20together%20was%20one%20thing%20but%20coding%20to%20get%20the%20alarm%20systems%20in%20place%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20essentially%20the%20first%20model%20I%20was%20ever%20building%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikhil%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20became%20savvy%20with%20the%20arduino%20%E2%80%94%20an%20open-source%20coding%20board%20%E2%80%94%20that%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20device%20to%20control%20their%20working.%E2%80%9D%20The%20journey%20was%20fraught%20with%20learning%20and%20spanned%20months%2C%20with%20Nikhil%20refining%20his%20coding%20skills%2C%20sharpening%20his%20technical%20palette%20and%20perfecting%20Meditel%20with%20each%20learning.%20He%20c