-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20the%20efforts%20and%20Tiwari%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20filled%20up%20with%20rainwater%20that%20lasted%20for%20a%20year%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355544%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20efforts%20of%20Tiwari%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20filled%20up%20with%20rainwater%20that%20lasted%20for%20a%20year%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPowering%20through%20opposition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20emphasises%20that%20getting%20acceptance%20of%20an%20idea%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20rungs%20of%20the%20ladder.%20But%20as%20you%20continue%20to%20ascend%20it%2C%20he%20says%2C%20conflict%20is%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20set%20out%20to%20do%20any%20positive%20work%2C%20there%20are%20three%20stages%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pass.%20The%20first%20is%20ridicule%2C%20where%20people%20will%20tell%20