20Bundela%20(%40romeeta_b)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ETO%2C%20or%20electrical%20officer%2C%20is%20responsible%20for%20all%20electrical%2C%20electronic%2C%20and%20control%20and%20automation%20systems%20onboard.%20They%20also%20manage%20reefers%20(cargo)%20on%20container%20vessels%2C%20explains%20the%20seafarer.%20In%20simple%20terms%2C%20they%20handle%20every%20electrical%20wire%20or%20cable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5BETOs%5D%20are%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20team%20as%20everything%20is%20getting%20automated%20including%20all%20systems%20onboard.%20We%20handle%20electrical%20and%20electronics%20equipment%2C%20power%20management%20system%2C%20control%20and%20automation%20system%2C%20marine%20and%20deck%20safety%20equipment%2C%20lighting%20system%2C%20along%20with%20refrigeration%20and%20ventilation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20glass%20%E2%80%98sea%E2%80%99ling%20on%20international%20waters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20the%20life%20of%20a%20seafarer%20is%20difficult.%20Being%20on%20a%20ship%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20away%20from%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20with%20movement%20restricted%20to%20the%20vessel%20is%20no%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Romeeta%20Bundela%20from%20Jalgaon%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20female%20Electro%20Technical%20Officer%20(ETO)%20on%20a%20Maersk%20ship%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERomeeta%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20female%20Electro%20Technical%20Officer%20(ETO)%20on%20a%20Maersk%20ship%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERomeeta%20recalls%20her%20first%20experience%20on%20a%20ship%20at%20Maersk.%20Her%20first%20contract%20was%20for%20four%20months%20and%20began%20from%20Singapore%20on%20a%20merchant%20vessel%20with%2020%20men.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20she%20received%20a%20cold%20welcome%20even%20before%20she%20could%20place%20her%20suitcase%20in%20her%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20manager%20had%20never%20seen%20a%20woman%20in%20this%20role.%20He%20was%20really%20dominating%20and%20kept%20telling%20me%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20job.%20It%20was%20extremely%20demotivating.%20Imagine%20listening%20to%20this%20all%20the%20time!%20I%20survived%20the%20four%20months%20and%20proved%20him%20wrong%20through%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20ETO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20proudly%20shares%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20first%20contract%2C%20the%20same%20manager%20who%20had%20initially%20judged%20her%20conducted%20her%20appraisal.%20He%20gave%20her%20a%20good%20recommendation%20and%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20wrong%20to%20judge%20you%20without%20seeing%20your%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20interviewed%20Romeeta%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20ponder%20how%20water%20has%20no%20ceiling%2C%20but%20even%20there%2C%20men%20have%20built%20a%20glass%20ceiling%2C%20which%20she%20successfully%20broke.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20gave%20you%20the%20strength%20and%20fortitude%20to%20face%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20colleagues%20were%20nice%20to%20me%20to%20my%20face%20but%20they%20all%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20not%20capable%20just%20because%20of%20my%20gender.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20this%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fadmin.php%3Fpage%3Dstats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproblem%20faced%20by%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20land%20jobs%20too%3F%20All%20you%20can%20do%20is%20focus%20and%20work%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20keeping%20her%20chin%20up%20and%20focusing%20on%20excelling%20at%20her%20job%2C%20she%20silenced%20all%20her%20critics.%20Girls%20can%20do%20everything%2C%20she%20proved%2C%20rather%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Romeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERomeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20she%20says%2C%20came%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20when%20she%20was%20stuck%20at%20sea%20for%20over%20nine%20months%20in%20China.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20she%20was%20on%20a%20cargo%20vessel%2C%20and%20with%20flights%20grounded%2C%20they%20had%20to%20stay%20on%20board%20and%20continue%20working.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20stuck%20in%20China%20and%20had%20to%20wear%20PPE%20kits%2C%20coveralls%2C%20and%20masks.%20Life%20was%20hell%20as%20we%20had%20no%20flights%20back%20home.%20It%20was%20mental%20torture%20for%20all%20of%20us%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20this%2C%20being%20on%20sea%20definitely%20comes%20with%20challenges%2C%20as%20you%20have%20to%20work%20in%20the%20engine%20room%20in%2050-55%20centigrade%20temperatures!%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20especially%20challenging%20during%20your%20%E2%80%98periods%E2%80%99.%20But%20I%20believe%20that%20you%20have%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20reach%20the%20top.%20A%20seafarer%20is%20a%20seafarer%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20gender%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20ability%20to%20rise%20above%20challenges%20led%20to%20rapid%20advancement%20in%20her%20career%2C%20as%20she%20progressed%20from%20ETO%20to%20senior%20ETO%20to%20electrical%20superintendent%20in%20just%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98At%20just%2026%2C%20I%20handled%2064%20vessels%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20first%20lady%20superintendent%20in%20Maersk%20and%20also%20the%20youngest%20one%20at%2026.%20I%20handled%2064%20vessels%20and%20provided%20electrical%20support%20and%20remote%20resolution.%20I%20was%20responsible%20for%20various%20projects%20such%20as%20LED%20lights%20in%20vessels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCr-xcm0tco4%2F%3Futm_sour